sources.title: The Manster (1959) HALF MAN-HALF MONSTER
sources.description:
It's FRIGHT NIGHT @PizzaFLIX 
Writer/Director: George P. Breakston
Stars: Peter Dyneley, Jane Hylton, Tetsu Nakamura

An American journalist in Japan becomes the unwitting subject of a reclusive scientist conducting bizarre experiments and begins a horrifying transformation after being injected with a strange serum.
